tps://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/tips-to-create-viral-content-marketing-strategy/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 17 Jul 2017 11:12:57 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:9:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"Search Engine Optimization\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Tips and Tricks\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"Content Marketing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"Content Marketing Strategy\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"seo\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"SEO Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Viral Content\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:7;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"Viral Content Marketing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:8;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"Viral Content Marketing Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/?p=22721\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:617:\"<p>Are you blogger or content marketer? Are you facing difficulty in making your content reach the potential readers? Read this article and get ready to create the right content that will go viral. I was inspired to write this article to help you marketers who are struggling to generate good traffic for your blog or [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/tips-to-create-viral-content-marketing-strategy/\">11 Most Effective Tactics to Make Your Content Go Viral</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Sanjay Dabhoya\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12180:\"<p>Are you blogger or content marketer? Are you facing difficulty in making your content reach the potential readers?</p>\n<p>Read this article and get ready to create the right content that will go viral. I was inspired to write this article to help you marketers who are struggling to generate good traffic for your blog or any other piece of information.</p>\n<p>You can follow these steps and you can also bring more traffic to your information just like any other popular blogger. Ofcourse, It will take some time as there is no shortcut to SEO. You might not see results overnight but if you maintain consistency and follow strategies you will see results.</p>\n<p>Being a content marketer, I had struggled many times to attract potential audience. I can understand the pain of not attracting the audience to the content that took almost 20 to 40 hours of efforts in writing. With years of experience, our team have analysed, what type of content can get attention and what fails. So here we have listed the things that can be useful next time you create a content.</p>\n<p><strong>So, how will you create a content that goes Viral?</strong></p>\n<p>This is very important question and answer is needed. With “VIRAL” I mean the content that is spread quickly or shared with large number of audience. I am sure that many of you are trying to get the answer. By far,  we have concluded few things that will help you to create a shareable content. Lets start then:</p>\n<h3>1. Research</h3>\n<p>Find out what people like around your niche topic in social media channels like <strong>Facebook, Twitter, Google Plus</strong> or any other content channels. Social channels lets you find the live topics discussed among real audience. Read some of those topics and think what type of posts you would like to share or comment. A content should include combination any of the below mentioned perspectives :</p>\n<p>1) Interest<br />\n2) Humor, Sadness<br />\n3) News<br />\n4) Latest Trends<br />\n5) Information<br />\n6) Inspirational<br />\n7) Free downloads<br />\n8) How to and DIY things<br />\n9) Polls and Feedbacks</p>\n<h3>2. Catchy Headlines</h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_27324\" style=\"width: 576px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Catchy-Headlines.gif\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Catchy-Headlines.gif\" alt=\"Catchy Headlines\" width=\"566\" height=\"312\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27324\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Catchy Headlines</p></div>\n<p>8 out of 10 readers will skip reading your content, if your headline is not enough to catch the attention. So without a doubt, headline is the first thing to be taken care of while writing content. This will literally make or break your reader base. You can write headlines in numbered format like:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/top-free-magento-2-themes-extensions/\" target=\"_blank\">Top Free Magento 2 Theme and Extensions For Your Magento Store</a><br />\nOr in a question format like:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/top-free-magento-2-themes-extensions/\" target=\"_blank\">Are You Looking for Free Magento 2 Extensions and Themes?</a></p>\n<h3>3. Invoking Emotions</h3>\n<p>Personally, I have felt that sometimes, I am energised with positive thoughts or posts on any social media channels. You can invoke emotions in your readers with any story that makes them happy or sad after reading your posts. It is very easy to write an informative post, but it takes a bit of creativity to infuse humour or sadness in your content. Our team at Solwin Infotech is skilled with such creativity, just call them and discuss about your topic.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_27331\" style=\"width: 650px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Invoking-Emotions.jpg\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Invoking-Emotions.jpg\" alt=\"Invoking Emotions\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27331\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Invoking-Emotions.jpg 640w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Invoking-Emotions-300x200.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Invoking-Emotions-500x333.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Invoking-Emotions-366x245.jpg 366w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Invoking-Emotions-624x415.jpg 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Invoking Emotions</p></div>\n<h3>4. Be The First One To Announce The News</h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_28579\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Be-The-First-One-To-Announce-The-News.jpeg\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Be-The-First-One-To-Announce-The-News.jpeg\" alt=\"Be The First One To Announce The News\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" class=\"size-full wp-image-28579\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Be-The-First-One-To-Announce-The-News.jpeg 800w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Be-The-First-One-To-Announce-The-News-300x169.jpeg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Be-The-First-One-To-Announce-The-News-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Be-The-First-One-To-Announce-The-News-500x281.jpeg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Be-The-First-One-To-Announce-The-News-624x351.jpeg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Be-The-First-One-To-Announce-The-News-350x197.jpeg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Image source: Buffer.com</p></div>\n<p>Talking about news, I would like to draw your attention regarding the latest news of Demonetization of 500 and 100 Notes in India. Yes, while I am writing this content, our PM has announced the ban on using these high currency notes. If you use <a href=\"https://www.google.com/alerts\" target=\"_blank\">Google news alerts</a> or RSS feeds of any news channels, you will be the first one to pass on the news to local audiences who are unaware of the news. You can create a content using that news and implementing your own opinions and views on that. This way you are catching attention first. You readers will gradually trust your blog as they got to know about something which was shared by you first. They will definitely share your content to their friends and family.</p>\n<p><strong>You can grab such hot topics to write. Creating viral content is quite a difficult  task as it involves open ears and observations to the information and latest trends around you.  But it is not impossible, If you are a good writer. You can also <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">approach us</a> at Solwin Infotech for creating such viral contents. Our content writing services are very affordable.</strong></p>\n<p>Anyway, coming back to our strategies. Remember always, your content can also solve a particular question or problem. If a visitor finds solution with your posts, he/she will definitely come back to your blog. If you or your team are skilled at solving any problems like any technical issues of Lenovo laptops or mobiles. Record a video and share it on <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a>.</p>\n<h3>5. Stay Up-To-Date</h3>\n<p>It is necessary to stay in tune with what is going around. Read and follow other&#8217;s blogs and news around internet. Participate in forums and groups to stay up-to-date with all the latest talks. You can interact, share your views on other&#8217;s posts.</p>\n<h3>6. Which Channel Works For You?</h3>\n<p>Once you start practicing, reading and participating in blogs and forums, you can analyze, which channel helps you to generate visitors. There are so many social channels like Scoopit, Blogs, Reddif, <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SolwinInfotech\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a>, Online magazines etc.. Publish your contents on these channels and check which media is bringing you more and more visitors. You can also do guest blogging and make your content viral. The traffic coming to that blog will be diverted to your post.</p>\n<blockquote><p>We don&#8217;t have a choice on whether we do social media, the question is how well we do it? ― Erik Qualman</p></blockquote>\n<h3>7. Inter-Link Your Posts</h3>\n<p>You can interlink your other channels, once you know which channel is getting you the most traffic. This way you can focus on any specific channel and thus bringing traffic to your other channels. Analyse the list of topics, which attracted more visitors and use its link in other articles.</p>\n<h3>8. Interaction And Communication</h3>\n<p>Using polls and contact forms on your blog is the best way to stay in touch with your audience. Try Solwin Infotech&#8217;s free <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/easy-contact-form-widget-magento-2/\" target=\"_blank\">CONTACT FORM extension</a> on your blog. If you receive any inquiry or feedback from any reader, do not miss to reach them by writing a thank you email to them. Replying your reader&#8217;s comments is also a best way to connect them personally. This way your readers will feel like attended and they will entice to read and comment more on your posts.</p>\n<h3>9. Free Downloads And Resources</h3>\n<p>Free things are always the center of attraction. You can give your readers a link to a free resource which your readers can use it whenever they want. Like for example, A free PDF which can include some tips or tricks of make up for party.</p>\n<h3>10. Use Images</h3>\n<p>You all are very well aware of this saying, “A picture speaks thousand words” Try using a MEME or high definition picture that relates to your content. I have found gif image has been used a lot in almost all contents and articles of 2017. Some stats or graphs like gold price visual might attract your visitors. Visually rich posts is awesome.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_28585\" style=\"width: 582px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/use-of-images.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/use-of-images.png\" alt=\"use of images\" width=\"572\" height=\"619\" class=\"size-full wp-image-28585\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/use-of-images.png 572w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/use-of-images-277x300.png 277w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/use-of-images-500x541.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/use-of-images-185x200.png 185w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Image source: incisive-edge.com</p></div>\n<h3>11. Information</h3>\n<p>Warnings, trends, tips and tricks are some type of information which can entice your readers. Just read and research around internet, magazines and you can share all those informations. Like you can share an informational post regarding an IT FAIR or EXHIBITION about which you read in newspaper last morning. Share your visit experience to any location, you have been recently.</p>\n<p>So, these were some tips to write a creative content. However, not even the news channels or newspapers know, which news or content will be super-hit. So keep trying these things. You may fail several times but you will surely succeed at some point.</p>\n<p><strong>Happy writing <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.2.1/72x72/1f642.png\" alt=\"?\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></strong></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/tips-to-create-viral-content-marketing-strategy/\">11 Most Effective Tactics to Make Your Content Go Viral</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/tips-to-create-viral-content-marketing-strategy/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:47:\"It’s Official – Magento Meetup now @ Surat!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/news/official-magento-meetup-now-surat/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:84:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/news/official-magento-meetup-now-surat/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 09 Jun 2017 13:05:53 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"Magento Community\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Magento Meetup\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"Magento Meetup Surat\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"Surat Magento Meetup\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"Surat Magento Meetup Group\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/?p=27434\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:602:\"<p>It was a mere thought until it turned into reality! The Magento Live India 2017 event held at Bengaluru made a lasting impact on our minds as we saw several Magento enthusiasts from different parts of India coming to Bengaluru to learn and know more about the offerings of the Magento community. We strongly felt [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/news/official-magento-meetup-now-surat/\">It&#8217;s Official &#8211; Magento Meetup now @ Surat!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Sanjay Dabhoya\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4734:\"<p>It was a mere thought until it turned into reality!</p>\n<p>The Magento Live India 2017 event held at Bengaluru made a lasting impact on our minds as we saw several Magento enthusiasts from different parts of India coming to Bengaluru to learn and know more about the offerings of the Magento community. We strongly felt that the magnificence of this community should reach to different parts of India.</p>\n<p>However, the seeds of developing local platforms for Magento were sown during the Magento Live India 2017 &#8216;Pre-event meet&#8217; where few of us were casually discussing with some of the Senior Magento team members and community members like Sherrie Rohde (Community Manager), Max Yekaterynenko (Director of Community Engineering), Eugene Tulika (Evangelist), Oleksii Korshenko (Software Architect), Talesh Seeparsan, Ramesh Kumar, Vijay Golani and few others about the idea of expanding the Magento community to different parts of India. Little did we know, that it was going to turn into reality so soon.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">A bunch of us are seated outside the Library Bar at Leela Palace for a Pre <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/MLIN17?src=hash\">#MLIN17</a> hangout. Come drop by. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/realmagento?src=hash\">#realmagento</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/vrfvSGkqK1\">pic.twitter.com/vrfvSGkqK1</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Talesh Seeparsan (@_Talesh) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/_Talesh/status/859023791489507329\">May 1, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>Solwin Infotech takes pleasure in announcing that Surat city is the latest to join the wagon of setting up Magento Meetup groups in different cities of India. Surat now has a Magento Meetup Group of its own. We encourage Magento enthusiasts from Surat and South Gujarat region (Ankaleshwar, Bharuch, Bardoli, Vyara, Navsari, Bilimora, Valsad, Vapi etc) to come and experience the offerings and latest happenings from around the world in Magento. If you are a beginner in Magento, it will surely be a delight for you to learn and know a lot more about Magento. If you are an expert, then you can play the role of a speaker and cascade your knowledge among others. The schedules for events will be released from time to time on the official <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Surat-Magento-Meetup\" target=\"_blank\">Surat Magento Meetup Group</a> page.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Surat-Magento-Meetup-page.png\" alt=\"Surat Magento Meetup page\" width=\"1073\" height=\"702\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-27500\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Surat-Magento-Meetup-page.png 1073w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Surat-Magento-Meetup-page-300x196.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Surat-Magento-Meetup-page-768x502.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Surat-Magento-Meetup-page-1024x670.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Surat-Magento-Meetup-page-500x327.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Surat-Magento-Meetup-page-624x408.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Surat-Magento-Meetup-page-850x556.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Surat-Magento-Meetup-page-306x200.png 306w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1073px) 100vw, 1073px\" /></p>\n<p>This wouldn&#8217;t have been possible without the support of Max Yekaterynenko (Director of Community Engineering), Eugene Tulika (Evangelist) and Taleesh Seeparsan. Special thanks to Sherrie Rohde (Community Manager) for the providing the approval.</p>\n<p>Solwin Infotech is privileged and ready to take this baton ahead in spreading the awareness of the offerings of Magento Community in our city through the Magento Meetup Surat. We think this is a great way of contributing to the Magento community.</p>\n<p>We are 39 members as of now and positive that the number will increase as more and more people become aware about this initiative.</p>\n<p>We think this is great step to strengthen the Magento roots in India. Lets join the Hands and share about <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Surat-Magento-Meetup/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Surat Magento Meetup Group</strong></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/news/official-magento-meetup-now-surat/\">It&#8217;s Official &#8211; Magento Meetup now @ Surat!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/news/official-magento-meetup-now-surat/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"WordPress Version 4.8 Released! Here’s Our Themes Compatibility Report\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/wordpress-4-8-themes-compatibility-report/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:97:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/wordpress-4-8-themes-compatibility-report/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 09 Jun 2017 07:39:32 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:8:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"WordPress 4.8\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"WordPress 4.8 Compatible Themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"WordPress 4.8 Themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"WordPress 4.8 Update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"WordPress Themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:7;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"WordPress v4.8\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/?p=27263\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:658:\"<p>The latest version of WordPress 4.8 has been released yesterday. We make it a priority to always keep our WordPress themes up-to-date, so that our customers can easily switch on latest update of WordPress without any issues. What&#8217;s bundled with WordPress 4.8? WordPress 4.8 adds some great new features to gear up for more intuitive [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/wordpress-4-8-themes-compatibility-report/\">WordPress Version 4.8 Released! Here’s Our Themes Compatibility Report</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Sanjay Dabhoya\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3050:\"<p>The latest version of WordPress 4.8 has been released yesterday. We make it a priority to always keep our WordPress themes up-to-date, so that our customers can easily switch on latest update of WordPress without any issues.</p>\n<h2>What&#8217;s bundled with WordPress 4.8?</h2>\n<p>WordPress 4.8 adds some great new features to gear up for more intuitive WordPress!</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Introduced 3 new widgets &#8211; Image, Video and Audio Widget</li>\n<li>Rich Text Editor with Text Widget</li>\n<li>Link Boundaries update with hyperlinks</li>\n<li>New Admin Dashboard Widget &#8211; WordPress Events and News</li>\n<li>And much more with security updates</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We had started preparation when first RC1 was available and then after we keep updating our themes to be compatible with next WordPress version 4.8. Today, we have published new updates to <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/products/wordpress-themes/\">all of our WordPress themes</a> by taking advantage of the new features WordPress 4.8 offers, both behind the scenes and in the forefront.</p>\n<p>I can confirm that Solwin Infotech&#8217;s every WordPress themes is 100% compatible with WordPress 4.8. There were a few issues that we’ve resolved, though they were very small and unlikely to occur. We have also taken a bit of time to tidy some of the older themes update with latest features in the catalogue.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">WordPress 4.8 “Evans” with community events tie-in, media widgets, improved visual editor,… <a href=\"https://t.co/OkT8mm6ACF\">https://t.co/OkT8mm6ACF</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/m0RFmGoyb9\">pic.twitter.com/m0RFmGoyb9</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; WordPress (@WordPress) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/WordPress/status/872828027683704832\">June 8, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>If you’re interested in reading a bit more on the new bits of WordPress version 4.8, check out the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/2017/06/evans/\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress 4.8</a> Field Guide. As usual, if you run into anything, let me know. Enjoy!</p>\n<h3>Further Reading:</h3>\n<p>So ideally you&#8217;ve discovered some new information today! In case you&#8217;re delighted, I definitely suggest perusing these two articles as well:</p>\n<p>1. <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/super-tips-to-choose-perfect-theme-for-your-wordpress-blog-or-website/\">Tips to Choose Perfect WordPress Theme</a><br />\n2. <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/tips-and-tricks/showcase-your-profile-picture-in-wordpress-website-without-gravatar/\">Showcase Profile Picture in WordPress without Gravatar Account</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/wordpress-4-8-themes-compatibility-report/\">WordPress Version 4.8 Released! Here’s Our Themes Compatibility Report</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/wordpress-4-8-themes-compatibility-report/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"6\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"Magento Live India 2017 – An Experience to Cherish for a Lifetime!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:98:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/ecommerce/magento-live-india-2017-experience-cherish-lifetime/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:107:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/ecommerce/magento-live-india-2017-experience-cherish-lifetime/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 08 May 2017 12:46:13 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:9:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"eCommerce\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Events\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"Magento Event India\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"Magento Live 2017\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"Magento Live Banglore\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"Magento Live India 2017\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:7;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Solwin Infotech at Magento Live\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:8;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"Top Magento Events 2017\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/?p=26607\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:659:\"<p>The grand ballroom of Leela Palace, Bengaluru saw humongous energy and enthusiasm pouring in from different parts of the world on 2nd May 2017. The occasion was equally significant as the place was hosting the first ever Magento Live, India 2017 event. It was an out-an out privilege to have closely witnessed this magnificent event. [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/ecommerce/magento-live-india-2017-experience-cherish-lifetime/\">Magento Live India 2017 – An Experience to Cherish for a Lifetime!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Sanjay Dabhoya\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13489:\"<p>The grand ballroom of Leela Palace, Bengaluru saw humongous energy and enthusiasm pouring in from different parts of the world on 2nd May 2017. The occasion was equally significant as the place was hosting the first ever Magento Live, India 2017 event. It was an out-an out privilege to have closely witnessed this magnificent event.</p>\n<p>It was great to see Magento developers, agencies and partners to come under one roof to meet and share the ideas and know what lies ahead for the Magento community.</p>\n<h3>Pre-Event Buzz</h3>\n<p>The pre-event get together arranged by Ramesh Kumar. He set the tone of energy for the next day&#8217;s main event. Few of Magento enthusiasts met and were enjoying outside the library bar and were waiting for others to join us.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">A bunch of us are seated outside the Library Bar at Leela Palace for a Pre <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/MLIN17?src=hash\">#MLIN17</a> hangout. Come drop by. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/realmagento?src=hash\">#realmagento</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/vrfvSGkqK1\">pic.twitter.com/vrfvSGkqK1</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Talesh Seeparsan (@_Talesh) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/_Talesh/status/859023791489507329\">May 1, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>Euguen Tulika, <span class=\"conversation_msg conmsg\"><span class=\"msgg\"> Ievgen Shakhsuvarov, Oleksii Korshenko and Sherrie Rohde soon joined us there.</span></span></p>\n<p>Later, we moved in where we were joined by Mark Lavelle, CEO, Magento commerce, Mark Lenhard, SVP Strategy and Growth, Jason Woosley, SVP, Technology &amp; Product, Max Yekaterynenko, Director of Community Engineering, Ben Marks and Andy Barker for drinks where Mark Lavelle took a selfie with all the attendees.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Thanks for making it happen Ramesh!  <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/MLIN17?src=hash\">#MLIN17</a> is now officially underway!! <a href=\"https://t.co/Xmv0YtwTf5\">pic.twitter.com/Xmv0YtwTf5</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Mark Lavelle (@mklave1) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mklave1/status/859046598642454528\">May 1, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>Everyone dispersed slowly, I too moved away and to my surprise it was raining profusely outside in the peak summers in India. Then someone informed me that it&#8217;s a normal scene to see in Bengaluru.</p>\n<h3>On the Big day @ the Registration desk</h3>\n<p>The first stop before the session began was at the registration desk where we received our Identity cards and we dropped our visiting cards too. I was pleased to meet the vibrant personality, Taleesh Seeparsan again there. We had met the previous day at the library bar.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">First Selfie at registration desk <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/mlin17?src=hash\">#mlin17</a> with always laughing guy <a href=\"https://twitter.com/_Talesh\">@_Talesh</a>  <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolwinInfotech\">@SolwinInfotech</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Magento2?src=hash\">#Magento2</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/sxykZi0nLd\">pic.twitter.com/sxykZi0nLd</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Sanjay Dabhoya (@sanjaydabhoya) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/sanjaydabhoya/status/859635074513469440\">May 3, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<h3>Ready to see the action</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Ready-for-action-Magento-Live-17.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-26783 size-full\" src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Ready-for-action-Magento-Live-17.jpg\" alt=\"Solwin Infotech team ready for action Magento Live 17\" width=\"820\" height=\"440\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Ready-for-action-Magento-Live-17.jpg 820w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Ready-for-action-Magento-Live-17-300x161.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Ready-for-action-Magento-Live-17-768x412.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Ready-for-action-Magento-Live-17-500x268.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Ready-for-action-Magento-Live-17-624x335.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Ready-for-action-Magento-Live-17-350x188.jpg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The event saw the presence of biggies from the Global Magento Team &#8211;<br />\nMark Lavelle, CEO, Magento Commerce,<br />\nMark Lenhard, SVP, Strategy and Growth<br />\nJason Woosley, SVP, Technology &amp; Product<br />\nMax Yekaterynenko, Director of Community Engineering<br />\nSherrie Rohde, Community Manager<br />\nand a few other senior members from the Magento Commerce team alongwith Anupam Pahuja, MD, Pay Pal India.</p>\n<p>Mark Lenhard&#8217;s kickstarted the event highlighting the contributions made by the Magento community in India. He introduced and invited on stage Mark Lavelle, CEO of Magento Commerce.</p>\n<p>Mark Lavelle took over the stage and presented certain statistics, growth projections about APAC e-commerce and the profound presence of mobile commerce in APAC region and what lies in the future for Magento community. Apart from his insightful presentation what caught everyone&#8217;s eye was his orange colored Modi jacket and greetings of “Namaste India” in the beginning of the session.</p>\n<p>One of the few key takeaways from his session was &#8220;Key to the success&#8221;<br />\n1] Be bold with your brand<br />\n2] Embrace digital first<br />\n3] Build flexibility into business<br />\n4] Innovate through human ingenuity</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Key to success <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mklave1\">@mklave1</a> at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/mlin17?src=hash\">#mlin17</a> excellent takeout of session <a href=\"https://t.co/T3qsVq2cpJ\">pic.twitter.com/T3qsVq2cpJ</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Sanjay Dabhoya (@sanjaydabhoya) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/sanjaydabhoya/status/859276220239929344\">May 2, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>The next session as per the schedule, we attended was by Vijay Golani, Magento U Trainer and Vice President of Development, Wagento where he threw light on the development concepts behind the functions, design, and workings of the Magento 2 platform.</p>\n<p>However, it was Talesh Seeparsan&#8217;s words which took my energy to the next level. It made me wonder if it was either in reciprocation to a small gesture towards him at the registration desk or my activeness and keenness throughout the event that made an impression in his mind. Anyways, thanks Taleesh.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Meeting so many skilled &amp; insightful members from the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/realmagento?src=hash\">#realmagento</a> India community at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/MLIN17?src=hash\">#MLIN17</a> like <a href=\"https://twitter.com/sanjaydabhoya\">@sanjaydabhoya</a>. You should follow him <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/2.2.1/72x72/1f60a.png\" alt=\"?\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n<p>&mdash; Talesh Seeparsan (@_Talesh) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/_Talesh/status/859288699267420161\">May 2, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>There was a session by Max Yekaterynenko, Director of Community Engineering, Magento Commerce on &#8220;Successful Migrations on Magento&#8221; simultaneously in another room.</p>\n<p>After Vijay&#8217;s session the next session we attended was by Ben Marks, Evangelist, Magento Commerce on Extension Development Best Practices and Marketplace EQP where he informed about some best tricks and tips for fast selling.</p>\n<p>After this session was lunch break, where we again took the opportunity of interacting with several attendees at length, clicking pictures and exploring the place little closely in the spare time after lunch.</p>\n<p>Post lunch, Jason Woosley, SVP of Product &amp; Technology, Magento Commerce and Max Yekaterynenko did a technical deep dive and showed us the ways in which we can make our business more powerful. He gave an overview of some of the key features Magento 2.2’s below:</p>\n<p>1] Magento Business Intelligence (BI)<br />\n2] Magento B2B Preview<br />\n3] Magento Shipping</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Presentation of Magento BI at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/mlin17?src=hash\">#mlin17</a> by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jasonwoosley_mg\">@jasonwoosley_mg</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/maksek_ua\">@maksek_ua</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/TxTSZGSFIB\">pic.twitter.com/TxTSZGSFIB</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Eugene Tulika (@vrann) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/vrann/status/859328287432208384\">May 2, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>We heard from few fellow members about an amazing session “Enhancing Your Career with The Magento Ecosystem” delivered by Sherry Rohde, Community Manager, Magento Ecommerce simultaneously in another room.</p>\n<p>Oleksii Korshenko, Software Architect, Magento Commerce delivered the next session on concept of backwards compatibility and its implications in case of Magento 2.</p>\n<p>Simultaneously, Ian Kinsella, Senior Director, Sales, APAC, Magento Commerce &amp; Ben Marks, Evangelist, Magento Commerce delivered a session on &#8220;Navigating Magento Commerce Order Management&#8221; in another room.</p>\n<p>Next session we attended in mid afternoon was “First Steps to Building Secure Magento Extensions” delivered by Taleesh Seeparsan, who touched an important aspect that is “Security” in the web-space. He admitted the fact that website are susceptible to hacking whereas at the same time created awareness about various strategies and tools that can be use to deal with “hacking”</p>\n<p>In a simultaneous session, Ben Marks talked about Business intelligence.</p>\n<h3>Final Session of the Day</h3>\n<p>The last session of the evening we attended was by Max Yekaterynenko, Director of Community Engineering, Magento Commerce where he talked about Magento 2 architectural directions and community contributions.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/maksek_ua\">@maksek_ua</a> on what our team is doing: enables commminity, encreases transparency and helps with contributions <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/mlin17?src=hash\">#mlin17</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/MagentoCommEng?src=hash\">#MagentoCommEng</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/MqjldCBUW1\">pic.twitter.com/MqjldCBUW1</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Eugene Tulika (@vrann) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/vrann/status/859366646317797376\">May 2, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>The event concluded with Mark Lavelle announcing that Magento Live will be back in 2018, Thus keeping the enthusiasm intact of the people</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Just announced: Magento Live coming back to India in 2018. Made possible by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/MLIN17?src=hash\">#MLIN17</a> Sponsors &amp; 500+ Attendees. Thank you! <a href=\"https://twitter.com/magento\">@magento</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/MLIN18?src=hash\">#MLIN18</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/hfnr39tu6j\">pic.twitter.com/hfnr39tu6j</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Mark Lavelle (@mklave1) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mklave1/status/859293563821195264\">May 2, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>After Mark&#8217;s announcement, the crowd was thrilled and overjoyed to know about the return of Magento Live in 2018. There were discussions and laughs amongst the people everywhere in the ballroom. Needless to say it was accompanied by bulk of selfies by almost everyone present there.</p>\n<p>The excitement was taken ahead to the after-party and dinner where people happily gorged on the delicious food and drinks and met each other before signing off.</p>\n<p>We managed to get hold of Mark Lavelle, CEO Magento Commerce and Mark Lenhard, SVP Strategy &amp; Growth, Magento Commerce amidst the crowd for a few minutes and surprisingly both of them asked me the same question &#8220;How was the event&#8221;? I was awe-struck and running short of words to express how delighted I was, but finally I managed to answer saying &#8211; &#8220;It was amazing&#8230;.!&#8221;</p>\n<p>Eagerly looking forward to Magento Live India 2018!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/ecommerce/magento-live-india-2017-experience-cherish-lifetime/\">Magento Live India 2017 – An Experience to Cherish for a Lifetime!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:103:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/ecommerce/magento-live-india-2017-experience-cherish-lifetime/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"Tips to Choose Perfect Theme for Your WordPress Blog or Website\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:116:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/super-tips-to-choose-perfect-theme-for-your-wordpress-blog-or-website/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:125:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/super-tips-to-choose-perfect-theme-for-your-wordpress-blog-or-website/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sat, 15 Apr 2017 03:49:39 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:7:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Tips and Tricks\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"Perfect WordPress Blog Theme\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"Tips to Choose Perfect Blog Theme\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"wordpress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"WordPress Blog Theme\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"WordPress Themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/?p=25457\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:632:\"<p>We all know that how overwhelmed and excited one is when they are looking for website or blog theme, especially if that is the first online platform for them. WordPress is an amazing yet easy to set up platform to build up your website. However it is not easy to choose a theme quickly because [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/super-tips-to-choose-perfect-theme-for-your-wordpress-blog-or-website/\">Tips to Choose Perfect Theme for Your WordPress Blog or Website</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"khushbu padalia\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5137:\"<p>We all know that how overwhelmed and excited one is when they are looking for website or blog theme, especially if that is the first online platform for them. </p>\n<blockquote><p>WordPress is an amazing yet easy to set up platform to build up your website.</p></blockquote>\n<p>However it is not easy to choose a theme quickly because there are so many paid and free themes available on internet today. All those themes are designed with aim to fit your business category. Each theme looks better than the other. So how can you know, <strong>which theme is perfect for you?</strong> And it is really important to choose a suitable theme because it affects overall performance of your website. </p>\n<p>From the background colour, font type, font colour and font size to the margin size and widget positions, your website or blog theme will determine how it will appear to visitors.</p>\n<p>So, the first question that may come to your mind is: <strong>Should I go for free theme or paid theme?</strong></p>\n<p>Well, with <strong>3000 free themes</strong> available on WordPress, anyone would lure to go for free theme. But it is rightly said “There is no such thing as free”. Free themes comes with some limitations like lack of mobile responsiveness, color customizations etc etc.. </p>\n<blockquote><p>The main reason for not opting to a free theme is that lack of support.</p></blockquote>\n<p>It can be very difficult for you to get any help or support from theme creator. Hence we would always suggest you to go for a paid theme, unless you want to start a blog for your personal hobby or interest.</p>\n<p>Every website has its own aim of being in online world. This purpose will be affected with the type of theme you choose. So these tips will help every soon-to-be website owner to choose the <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/wordpress-themes/bloggers/\" target=\"_blank\">best WordPress theme for blog</a> or website.</p>\n<p><strong>There are three main things on which your choice depends:</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Budget:</strong> How much your pocket allows spending on theme? Paid themes are really not as costly as you think. Those premium themes are worth spending where you get good support and service.</p>\n<p><strong>Purpose:</strong> For what purpose you are building blog or website. If you just want to start it for sharing your life experiences or as a hobby you can opt for free theme.</p>\n<p><strong>Features needed:</strong> Check if the free theme is serving all the important features you needed for your blog or website. If you want awesome features like attractive landing page and pixel perfect mobile website, premium theme is your option.</p>\n<h3>What other technical aspects should be checked while choosing WordPress theme:</h3>\n<p><strong>An SEO friendly structure:</strong> Make sure that Google loves and understands the theme you are using. In short, the theme should be SEO friendly to sustain in Search engine rankings.</p>\n<p><strong>Compatibility with every browser:</strong> Since your website is globally visible to all the visitors from all the corner of the world, you never know what browser they use. So check if your theme is supported by all browsers.</p>\n<p><strong>Customizable design:</strong> In nearly, all cases of themes, you will definitely tweak some of the default features to suit your personal choice of business. Check if the theme provides at least basic custom options.</p>\n<p><strong>Plugins:</strong> Choosing a theme that supports almost all major plugins to provide enhanced features and functionality can prevent you from getting trapped in theme.</p>\n<p><strong>Multilingual:</strong> If you are dealing with customers, suppliers and other businesses irrespective of their country, you have to make sure that your theme supports multi language. You need every single user to see your website in their native language.</p>\n<p><strong>Support:</strong> Double check if the company is offering extensive support for any issues regarding theme. Main advantage of premium theme is  certainly offer the best support, usually through a combination of a public forum, live chat and an email ticketing system.</p>\n<p><strong>Ratings:</strong> If the theme has a loophole then there will be lot of reviews placed by customers. However, the company might have overcome the issues raised by customers, you can get an idea of a theme’s overall quality while reading reviews.</p>\n<p>Make sure you pay attention to these recommendations and get the best theme for your website or blog.</p>\n<p>You can <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/hire-dedicated-developers/\">hire us</a> to install or customize a <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/products/wordpress-themes/\">WordPress theme</a> for you. You&#8217;re just going to love it!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/super-tips-to-choose-perfect-theme-for-your-wordpress-blog-or-website/\">Tips to Choose Perfect Theme for Your WordPress Blog or Website</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:121:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/super-tips-to-choose-perfect-theme-for-your-wordpress-blog-or-website/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"12\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:81:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"Best Practices For Kickass Call To Action Buttons\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/best-practices-kickass-call-action-buttons/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:92:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/best-practices-kickass-call-action-buttons/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 22 Mar 2017 13:42:13 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:14:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"Search Engine Optimization\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Tips and Tricks\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Call To Action\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"Call To Action Best Practice\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"Call To Action Buttons\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"Call To Action SEO\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"Call To Action Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:7;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Conversion\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:8;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"CTA\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:9;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"CTA Buttons\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:10;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"CTA Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:11;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"CTA Tricks\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:12;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"seo\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:13;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"SEO Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/?p=24000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:613:\"<p>So you have a great page with lots of amazing graphics and good content, still no actions?? Have you noticed your action driving elements closely? With action driving elements, we mean the buttons or links that converts a visitor into customer or permanent member. Today we will explain how to make your action buttons as [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/best-practices-kickass-call-action-buttons/\">Best Practices For Kickass Call To Action Buttons</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Anupam Bhagat\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10752:\"<p>So you have a great page with lots of amazing graphics and good content, still no actions?? </p>\n<p>Have you noticed your action driving elements closely? With action driving elements, we mean the <strong>buttons or links</strong> that converts a visitor into customer or permanent member. Today we will explain how to make your action buttons as persuasive as possible. </p>\n<p>It is really important <strong>to understand your goals as well as your demographics</strong>. You may loose building connection with your potential customer, if you are not using the <strong>right call to action word</strong>. The button should be enough magical and sending a straight away message to clients that they will take that critical decision to click the button. </p>\n<h2>So lets take a look at some NOT-TO-IGNORE steps for driving clicks on your call to action buttons:</h2>\n<h3>Appealing Colors:</h3>\n<p>Although it is the small element in comparison to whole landing page, it should have its own strong impact. So make sure, you <strong>design the button using attractive colors and shape</strong>, depending on your website&#8217;s theme. </p>\n<p>Use <strong>contrast colored button</strong> considering your webpage&#8217;s background color. Rounded buttons, rectangle buttons are common but you cannot deny that these shapes work for some. Try using these shapes and check which one is working for you. </p>\n<p>If you are going to follow this article in real terms, start with this piece of advice. Ask your web-designer to show you some samples of call-to-action buttons. Think yourself as a customer and choose which buttons catches your attention first.  You can read this article published in leading The guardian: <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2014/feb/05/why-google-engineers-designers\" target=\"_blank\">Why Google has put engineers over designers</a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Color matters, hence <a href=\"http://www.gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\">Gmail</a> tested shades of blue to check which one works for them.</p></blockquote>\n<h3>Powerful Words:</h3>\n<p>Strong words are that evoke emotions, should be used. Remember you don&#8217;t have enough room to write more content on the button, so <strong>find out the stronger verbs</strong> that will urge the customers to click right away. At the same time it should be short and sweet but conveying an emotion like “<strong>Let&#8217;s do it</strong>” instead of “<strong>get started</strong>”  </p>\n<p>With latest technologies like <strong>QR codes</strong>, it is even more easy to drive conversions. If you can offer scanning QR codes for your products and they will love it. Like, you can offer discounts on scanning QR codes besides your products. QR code is not a call to action button, but it will definitely lead your visitors to click on button placed around it.</p>\n<p>We came across <strong>Narendra Modi app</strong> which urged people to share their views on Demonetization. The wise marketing team might have thought that public will be lazy in visiting the play-store and then download the app. The <a href=\"http://www.narendramodi.com\" target=\"_blank\">www.narendramodi.com</a> website offered shortcut to scan the QR code and the app is accessible.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_24005\" style=\"width: 1241px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/namo.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/namo.png\" alt=\"Narendra Modi App\" width=\"1231\" height=\"701\" class=\"size-full wp-image-24005\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/namo.png 1231w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/namo-300x171.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/namo-768x437.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/namo-1024x583.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/namo-500x285.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/namo-624x355.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/namo-850x484.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/namo-350x200.png 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1231px) 100vw, 1231px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Narendra Modi App</p></div>\n<h3>Right Emplacement:</h3>\n<p>Location also plays important role in getting attention. Try putting your <strong>CTA buttons</strong> above the fold, below the fold or anywhere on your webpage and track which position is best. Although, position is not the matter if your page, product or service is compelling enough to convince customers. But we should not miss any opportunity, so try this one out. We placed the buttons <strong>above the fold</strong> because its free and we want customers to read that the <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/wordpress-themes/bloggers-lite/\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress blog theme</a> is available for FREE:</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_24006\" style=\"width: 1261px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Blogger-Free-WordPress-Theme.jpg\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Blogger-Free-WordPress-Theme.jpg\" alt=\"Blogger - Free WordPress Theme\" width=\"1251\" height=\"731\" class=\"size-full wp-image-24006\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Blogger-Free-WordPress-Theme.jpg 1251w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Blogger-Free-WordPress-Theme-300x175.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Blogger-Free-WordPress-Theme-768x449.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Blogger-Free-WordPress-Theme-1024x598.jpg 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Blogger-Free-WordPress-Theme-500x292.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Blogger-Free-WordPress-Theme-624x365.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Blogger-Free-WordPress-Theme-850x497.jpg 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Blogger-Free-WordPress-Theme-342x200.jpg 342w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1251px) 100vw, 1251px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Blogger &#8211; Free WordPress Theme</p></div>\n<h3>Perfect Timing:</h3>\n<p>Timing also matters the most for CTA buttons. With the increasing video commercials, you would like to <strong>show your customers what you offer</strong> and then quickly give them CTA button. Like watching an commercial on donating old clothes to orphanage, <strong>don&#8217;t just let them forget about it</strong>. Give them the button when the essence of the video is still on their mind.</p>\n<p>If your aim is to gain likes and fans on Social media platforms, connect them well using CTA buttons. <strong>Stop asking your visitors to like your page instead give them a reason why they should like your page</strong>. Introduce a button which says “<strong>Like &amp; get 10% OFF</strong>” This is called result oriented button. You are showing the result they will get when they like your page.</p>\n<blockquote><p>Want, Need, Save are few desires, you can focus upon.</p></blockquote>\n<h3>Negative Words:</h3>\n<p>While we researched some good marketing blogs, one of the biggest take away from Neil Patel&#8217;s blog is the negative words. Yes, negative words like <strong>“No, I don&#8217;t want this free PDF” will grab user&#8217;s attention twice</strong>. They will read that again at least to see what they are reading and the button is clearly stating that they are loosing the opportunity to get free PDF. For example see the image below:</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_24008\" style=\"width: 1206px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Neil-Patel-Blog.jpg\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Neil-Patel-Blog.jpg\" alt=\"Neil Patel Blog\" width=\"1196\" height=\"627\" class=\"size-full wp-image-24008\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Neil-Patel-Blog.jpg 1196w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Neil-Patel-Blog-300x157.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Neil-Patel-Blog-768x403.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Neil-Patel-Blog-1024x537.jpg 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Neil-Patel-Blog-500x262.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Neil-Patel-Blog-624x327.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Neil-Patel-Blog-850x446.jpg 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Neil-Patel-Blog-350x183.jpg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1196px) 100vw, 1196px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Neil Patel Blog</p></div>\n<h3>Act Emotionally:</h3>\n<p>Problem solving approach always work, even on buttons. Use words like <strong>“End your worries here&#8221;</strong>, “your” will make them feel like their own. If this is not working use “My or me” possessive words. “End my worries” will make them feel possessive and this may hit.</p>\n<p>You can also <strong>use time frame words</strong> on buttons like “<strong>Now, Today, Before, End</strong>”. For example “Grab now or miss it” “Get my free stuff today” Grab it before anyone else do” “Deal ending soon” . These phrases will force the customers to decide quickly. You can see that any of this button will ultimately make your customers decide now rather than later. </p>\n<blockquote><p>Do not give them time to think, just get them do it now!</p></blockquote>\n<p>What works for your audience, can only be determined after experimenting. Try these tricks and keep a track of what has helped more in conversions. Optimize as per the results you get by continuously testing it for few weeks or months. </p>\n<p>There is lot more on <strong>driving sales with call to action buttons</strong>, that we can discuss if you are interested. Our <strong>SEO team at Solwin Infotech</strong> can help you monitor your strategies of call-to-action buttons. At Solwin Infotech, We can design such crazy effective CTA buttons for you. <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">Reach us now</a>! Gear up for the next campaign, All the best, folks!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/best-practices-kickass-call-action-buttons/\">Best Practices For Kickass Call To Action Buttons</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/best-practices-kickass-call-action-buttons/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"6\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"How to Showcase Your Profile Picture in WordPress Website without Gravatar Account\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:120:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/tips-and-tricks/showcase-your-profile-picture-in-wordpress-website-without-gravatar/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:129:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/tips-and-tricks/showcase-your-profile-picture-in-wordpress-website-without-gravatar/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sat, 18 Mar 2017 04:44:21 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:7:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Tips and Tricks\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Gravatar\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"Gravatar Account\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"Profile Picture Without Gravatar\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"wordpress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"WordPress Gravatar\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/?p=24108\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:679:\"<p>Website presentation is not just limited to texts, it’s a combination of well organized texts and images. And specially for forum and blog showcase, it is very important to a person who had written it. Since long time we have been posting blogs on website without Gravatar and not showing actual author. But the new [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/tips-and-tricks/showcase-your-profile-picture-in-wordpress-website-without-gravatar/\">How to Showcase Your Profile Picture in WordPress Website without Gravatar Account</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Alkesh Miyani\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9927:\"<p>Website presentation is not just limited to texts, it’s a combination of well organized texts and images. And specially for forum and blog showcase, it is very important to a person who had written it.</p>\n<p>Since long time we have been posting blogs on website without Gravatar and not showing actual author. But the new trend started in the industry now. Let me explain the benefits of using Gravtar.</p>\n<p>Here are some important tips to use Gravtar right away.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://en.gravatar.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Gravatar</a> is a &#8220;Globally Recognized Avatar&#8221;. You can easily showcase your self site to site like comment, blog author, etc. You just need to create account, upload your profile picture and wait for few minutes to recognize your picture with connected email address. Yes, this profile picture can actually prove your branding and reader loyalty.</p>\n<h3>Benefits of using Gravatar:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Building your author brand</li>\n<li>Redirect visitors to same writer blogs</li>\n<li>Increase your authority</li>\n<li>Professional profile pic. showcase</li>\n</ul>\n<p>But, the question is that all of your website authors, guest authors or end users of your blog don’t know about this facility. We should guide them to use this great feature of WordPress. </p>\n<p>More questions &#8211; Why they are interested in this matter? Why they will create a new account just for image showcase? Why will they embed their email address for any other websites as well? </p>\n<p>Just because of all these reasons, you might loss the beauty of your website.</p>\n<p>Let me suggest, how you can go ahead to overcome this issue. I have selected our Blog Designer PRO plugin&#8217;s <a href=\"http://blogdesigner.solwininfotech.com/demo/blog-brit-co-blog-template/\" target=\"_blank\">Brit Co</a> Blog Template with Gravatar images.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_24261\" style=\"width: 830px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Brit-co-Blog-Page-with-only-Gravatar.jpg\" alt=\"Brit co Blog Template - Blog Designer PRO\" width=\"820\" height=\"332\" class=\"size-full wp-image-24261\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Brit-co-Blog-Page-with-only-Gravatar.jpg 820w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Brit-co-Blog-Page-with-only-Gravatar-300x121.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Brit-co-Blog-Page-with-only-Gravatar-768x311.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Brit-co-Blog-Page-with-only-Gravatar-500x202.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Brit-co-Blog-Page-with-only-Gravatar-624x253.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Brit-co-Blog-Page-with-only-Gravatar-350x142.jpg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Brit co Blog Page with only Gravatar</p></div>\n<p>Yes, have you noticed that some posts missing Gravatar images? and that’s why its looking with default “Mystery Man”. I have done some research to fill up this gap for bloggers and as a solution, I found some useful plugins that will give you Gravatar image control with WordPress website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/custom-user-profile-photo/\" target=\"_blank\">Custom User Profile Photo</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Custom-User-Profile-Photo.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Custom-User-Profile-Photo.png\" alt=\"Custom User Profile Photo - WordPress Plugin\" width=\"766\" height=\"246\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-24498\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Custom-User-Profile-Photo.png 766w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Custom-User-Profile-Photo-300x96.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Custom-User-Profile-Photo-500x161.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Custom-User-Profile-Photo-624x200.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Custom-User-Profile-Photo-350x112.png 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 766px) 100vw, 766px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Custom User Profile Photo is an essential plugin to give facility to end users as he/she can upload own profile pictures instead of Gravatar image. That profile picture will available within blog author showcase, comment author showcase, etc. like it will recognize with whole current WordPress site. Users can use different profile pictures in all WordPress websites.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-first-letter-avatar/\" target=\"_blank\">WP First Letter Avatar</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/WP-First-Letter-Avatar.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/WP-First-Letter-Avatar.png\" alt=\"WP First Letter Avatar - WordPress Plugin\" width=\"769\" height=\"246\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-24499\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/WP-First-Letter-Avatar.png 769w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/WP-First-Letter-Avatar-300x96.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/WP-First-Letter-Avatar-768x246.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/WP-First-Letter-Avatar-500x160.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/WP-First-Letter-Avatar-624x200.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/WP-First-Letter-Avatar-350x112.png 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 769px) 100vw, 769px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WP First Letter Avatar includes a set of beautiful, colorful letter avatars in many sizes. Optimal size will be chosen by the plugin in order to display high quality avatar instead of default one. This plugin will might be a single plugin solution for your WordPress site if you are fighting for Gravatars for your blog authors.  </p>\n<p>As per the image below, you can see that I have implemented both above plugins with my blog website. Now, its looking more beautiful and pretty as compared to the old one.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_24262\" style=\"width: 830px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Brit-co-Blog-Page-with-Gravatar-and-plugin-support.jpg\" alt=\"Brit co Blog Template - Blog Designer PRO\" width=\"820\" height=\"332\" class=\"size-full wp-image-24262\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Brit-co-Blog-Page-with-Gravatar-and-plugin-support.jpg 820w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Brit-co-Blog-Page-with-Gravatar-and-plugin-support-300x121.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Brit-co-Blog-Page-with-Gravatar-and-plugin-support-768x311.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Brit-co-Blog-Page-with-Gravatar-and-plugin-support-500x202.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Brit-co-Blog-Page-with-Gravatar-and-plugin-support-624x253.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Brit-co-Blog-Page-with-Gravatar-and-plugin-support-350x142.jpg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Brit co Blog Page with Gravatar and plugin support</p></div>\n<p>To see the live demo of Gravatar in action, please check our Blog Designer site&#8217;s demo layouts and add simply comments with the any blog posts and hope you will find some new faces with the blog. Our motto of this blog is that improve blog page design with the help of well known plugins which will give you advanced feature to your current blog page. </p>\n<h3>News: <a href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/blog-designer-pro-for-wordpress/17069678?ref=solwin\" target=\"_blank\">Blog Designer PRO</a> v1.5 is on the way!</h3>\n<p>We are going to announce official news about our next version of Blog Designer PRO v1.5 release in next few days. So, if you aren&#8217;t familiar with our Blog Designer plugin then please try <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/blog-designer/\" target=\"_blank\">this lite version</a> of Blog Designer plugin. It&#8217;s free download.</p>\n<h4>Upcoming Features in Version 1.5:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New Admin UI for better User Experience</li>\n<li>New Template: <a href=\"http://blogdesigner.solwininfotech.com/demo/blog-pretty-blog-template/\" target=\"_blank\">Pretty Blog Template</a></li>\n<li>New Template: <a href=\"http://blogdesigner.solwininfotech.com/demo/blog-tagly-blog-template/\" target=\"_blank\">Tagly Blog Template</a></li>\n<li>New Template: <a href=\"http://blogdesigner.solwininfotech.com/demo/blog-brite-blog-template/\" target=\"_blank\">Brite Blog Template</a></li>\n<li>New Template: <a href=\"http://blogdesigner.solwininfotech.com/demo/blog-chapter-blog-template/\" target=\"_blank\">Chapter Blog Template</a></li>\n<li>New Archive Type &#8211; Search Result page support</li>\n<li>Media Grid Template with multiple column options</li>\n</ul>\n<p>So, what are you waiting for now? Try the lite version and upgrade to PRO plugin before the price go high. From next month, we might update prices of <a href=\"https://codecanyon.net/user/solwin/portfolio\" target=\"_blank\">all our codecanyon products</a>.</p>\n<p>We wish you can take advantage of some of these last period price deals and yes, don&#8217;t forget to beautify your blog page with the above tricks that I mentioned earlier!!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/tips-and-tricks/showcase-your-profile-picture-in-wordpress-website-without-gravatar/\">How to Showcase Your Profile Picture in WordPress Website without Gravatar Account</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:125:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/tips-and-tricks/showcase-your-profile-picture-in-wordpress-website-without-gravatar/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"14\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"10 SEO Ranking Factors To Boost Google Rankings in 2017\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:90:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/10-seo-ranking-factors-boost-google-rankings-2017/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:99:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/10-seo-ranking-factors-boost-google-rankings-2017/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 07 Feb 2017 11:57:49 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:10:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"Search Engine Optimization\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"Social Media Marketing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Tips and Tricks\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"Boost Google Rankings\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Google Rankings\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"Google Rankings 2017\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"google+\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:7;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"seo\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:8;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"SEO Ranking Factors\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:9;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"SEO Ranking Factors 2017\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/?p=21737\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:640:\"<p>Now that you are done with developing your website, whats next? Next is catching Google&#8217;s ranking, which is quite tough. Make sure you read this article carefully so that you can understand the basics of getting in to Google&#8217;s ranking race. At Solwin Infotech, we have got many online shop owners who succeeded their online [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/10-seo-ranking-factors-boost-google-rankings-2017/\">10 SEO Ranking Factors To Boost Google Rankings in 2017</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Anupam Bhagat\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15903:\"<p>Now that you are done with developing your website, whats next? Next is catching Google&#8217;s ranking, which is quite tough. Make sure you read this article carefully so that you can understand the basics of getting in to Google&#8217;s ranking race.</p>\n<p>At <strong>Solwin Infotech</strong>, we have got many online shop owners who succeeded their online business, but there are some, who failed to make the most out of Google. With every project, we analyze and track down the factors that boosted one&#8217;s online presence. We also keep track of those who failed to perform in Search engines. Hence, in this article we are presenting some <strong>necessary basic steps that needs to follow to achieve Google rankings</strong>. If you have missed any of them, this is the chance you can improve your website&#8217;s Google rankings. If those are too technical for you, Solwin Infotech is here to help you.</p>\n<p>SEO is a gradual process and may take up-to months or years to get you good results. So do not panic, if you are not getting results quickly. Keep doing and you will see the results.</p>\n<h2><strong>Lets go through the list now:</strong></h2>\n<h3><strong>1) Well Designed Website:</strong></h3>\n<p> It is very important to have <strong>clean and attractively designed website</strong> to get attention of your audience. Who does not like to get into the coolest showroom with best flooring lights and decorative walls? Same is the case with online store, let your audience at least bring to your desktop website with its awesome look.<br />\n<div id=\"attachment_23220\" style=\"width: 690px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Well-Designed-Website.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Well-Designed-Website.png\" alt=\"Well Designed Website\" width=\"680\" height=\"746\" class=\"size-full wp-image-23220\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Well-Designed-Website.png 680w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Well-Designed-Website-273x300.png 273w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Well-Designed-Website-500x549.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Well-Designed-Website-624x685.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Well-Designed-Website-182x200.png 182w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Well Designed Website</p></div></p>\n<h3><strong>2) Mobile Responsive:</strong></h3>\n<p> With recent Google update, the big giant has made it clear that <strong>there is no room for websites which are not mobile-optimized</strong>. If you have not paid attention to your mobile responsive feature, its high time to ask your developer about it. We at Solwin Infotech offer mobile responsive designs and themes.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_23235\" style=\"width: 1284px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/mobile-responsive.jpeg\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/mobile-responsive.jpeg\" alt=\"Mobile Responsive Website\" width=\"1274\" height=\"690\" class=\"size-full wp-image-23235\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/mobile-responsive.jpeg 1274w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/mobile-responsive-300x162.jpeg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/mobile-responsive-768x416.jpeg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/mobile-responsive-1024x555.jpeg 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/mobile-responsive-500x271.jpeg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/mobile-responsive-624x338.jpeg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/mobile-responsive-850x460.jpeg 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/mobile-responsive-350x190.jpeg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1274px) 100vw, 1274px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Mobile Responsive Website</p></div>\n<h3><strong>3) Onpage Optimization:</strong></h3>\n<p> Ensure that you have listed the targeted keywords. Check its competition and impact on your website. You can check the keywords in Google Analytics here: <strong>Acquisition &gt; Search Console &gt; Queries</strong>. </p>\n<div id=\"attachment_23222\" style=\"width: 1596px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/ga-result.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/ga-result.png\" alt=\"Google Analytics Results\" width=\"1586\" height=\"692\" class=\"size-full wp-image-23222\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/ga-result.png 1586w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/ga-result-300x131.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/ga-result-768x335.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/ga-result-1024x447.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/ga-result-500x218.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/ga-result-624x272.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/ga-result-850x371.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/ga-result-350x153.png 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1586px) 100vw, 1586px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Google Analytics Results</p></div>\n<p>Make a list of <em>top ranked keywords</em> and if you don&#8217;t know how to connect analytics and webmasters visit this link: <a href=\"https://support.google.com/webmasters/answer/1120006?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.google.com/webmasters/</a>. Check if your product images have <strong>Alt tags</strong> and other<strong> meta data</strong>.</p>\n<h3><strong>4) Sitemap:</strong></h3>\n<p> <strong>Sitemap is a crucial element</strong> to connect with Google&#8217;s algorithm. It is a file where you have to list all the web pages of your website. With the help of sitemap, you can tell Google and other search engines about organization and structure of your website. Submit the sitemap file in <a href=\"https://www.google.com/webmasters/tools/\" target=\"_blank\">Google webmaster</a> and monitor the index level.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><iframe width=\"625\" height=\"352\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0GvWruhcmwY?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<h3><strong>5) Google Business:</strong></h3>\n<p> Local SEO is very important from small to large sized business. <a href=\"https://www.google.co.in/business/\" target=\"_blank\">Register your business</a> in Google maps and help customers locate in your city. Operational hours, services offered and other business details should needs to update. Boost your local marketing efforts to step up the international market. At Solwin Infotech, we can assist you in registering your business on map.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_23230\" style=\"width: 1178px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/google-business-page-1.jpeg\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/google-business-page-1.jpeg\" alt=\"Google Business Page – Solwin\" width=\"1168\" height=\"685\" class=\"size-full wp-image-23230\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/google-business-page-1.jpeg 1168w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/google-business-page-1-300x176.jpeg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/google-business-page-1-768x450.jpeg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/google-business-page-1-1024x601.jpeg 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/google-business-page-1-500x293.jpeg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/google-business-page-1-624x366.jpeg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/google-business-page-1-850x499.jpeg 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/google-business-page-1-341x200.jpeg 341w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1168px) 100vw, 1168px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Google Business Page – Solwin</p></div>\n<h3><strong>6) Content Management:</strong></h3>\n<p> Content still rules the list of Google ranking factors. <strong>Unique content with SEO optimized keywords</strong> will enhance your rankings. <strong>Remove duplicate content</strong> and improve quality of content on your website. If you own e-commerce website, try to <strong>write unique description for each product</strong>. Our content writer team can help you with this task.</p>\n<h3><strong>7) Nicely Designed Blog:</strong></h3>\n<p> Blogging is the best way to content marketing. With more and more interesting content on your blog, more pages are generated and indexed in Google. Do not just sell your products on blog, but try to provide interesting information which they would like to read and comment on. <strong>Blog is the best way to engage with your customers</strong>. Solwin infotech offers free blog deign plugin.<br />\nDownload from here: <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/wordpress-plugins/blog-designer/\" target=\"_blank\">Blog Designer WordPress Plugin</a></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_23224\" style=\"width: 1582px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Nicely-Designed-Blog.jpeg\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Nicely-Designed-Blog.jpeg\" alt=\"Nicely Designed Blog\" width=\"1572\" height=\"1607\" class=\"size-full wp-image-23224\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Nicely-Designed-Blog.jpeg 1572w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Nicely-Designed-Blog-293x300.jpeg 293w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Nicely-Designed-Blog-768x785.jpeg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Nicely-Designed-Blog-1002x1024.jpeg 1002w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Nicely-Designed-Blog-500x511.jpeg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Nicely-Designed-Blog-624x638.jpeg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Nicely-Designed-Blog-850x869.jpeg 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Nicely-Designed-Blog-196x200.jpeg 196w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1572px) 100vw, 1572px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nicely Designed Blog</p></div>\n<h3><strong>8) Social Media Networks:</strong></h3>\n<p> How can we miss this channel of getting traffic. Establish yourself on all social media platforms like <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SolwinInfotech\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/solwininfotech\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a>, Instagram etc.. Post content using hashtags(#), polls and competitions. The more followers and fans you have on your social media, the more brand awareness you will have. Hire <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/social-media-marketing-services/\" target=\"_blank\">social media marketing experts</a> for getting your business on social media with right strategies.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_23225\" style=\"width: 1081px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/fb-solwin.jpeg\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/fb-solwin.jpeg\" alt=\"Social Media Networks\" width=\"1071\" height=\"526\" class=\"size-full wp-image-23225\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/fb-solwin.jpeg 1071w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/fb-solwin-300x147.jpeg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/fb-solwin-768x377.jpeg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/fb-solwin-1024x503.jpeg 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/fb-solwin-500x246.jpeg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/fb-solwin-624x306.jpeg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/fb-solwin-850x417.jpeg 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/fb-solwin-350x172.jpeg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1071px) 100vw, 1071px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Social Media Networks</p></div>\n<h3><strong>9) Backlinks:</strong></h3>\n<p> Internal linking, external linking play an important role in boosting your rankings. <strong>Use appropriate keyword enrich anchor text</strong> to give you more and more backlinks. Don&#8217;t give up your backlinking strategy as you wont see any instant results. There are lots of <a href=\"http://www.directorycritic.com/free-directory-list.html\" target=\"_blank\">submission websites</a>, you can submit your website using your targeted keywords and gain backlinks as much as you can. <em>Remember overdoing may lead to Spamming. Google may penalize you for this. </em>Our SEO experts is skilled at generating backlinks without getting penalized. Watch this video about overview of backlinks and its types.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><iframe width=\"625\" height=\"352\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/7U8rbnirU_k?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Source: omt365.com</strong></p>\n<h3><strong>10) Schema:</strong></h3>\n<p> <strong>Schema markup is microcode (semantic vocabulary)</strong> that is to be implemented on your website to help the search engines return more informative results for users. If you want to know in detail about this structured data, visit the central home <a href=\"http://www.schema.org\" target=\"_blank\">www.schema.org</a></p>\n<h3>Bonus Tip:</h3>\n<h3><strong>Gogole RankBrain: (One of the most important factor)</strong></h3>\n<p>RankBrain is Google’s name for a <strong>machine-learning artificial intelligence system</strong>. It helps Google in interpreting the queries that people insert in search box that might not have the exact words that were searched for. Enge says that <strong>it is the third most important signal</strong> among 100s of signals of the search engine. Google has said that <a href=\"http://searchengineland.com/faq-all-about-the-new-google-rankbrain-algorithm-234440\" target=\"_blank\">RankBrain</a> runs on all queries including broad and generic keywords, but it has a big impact on long tail keywords. Here are those sources about the Google RankBrain algorithm.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><iframe width=\"625\" height=\"352\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/z-NMIuhoyuE?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Source: bloomberg.com</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Conclusion:</strong><br />\nAt the end, I want to say that you should optimize your site according to these top 10 ranking factors. Remember that if you make your client like your content, you will get higher rankings in Google for any keyword naturally.  </p>\n<p>So, be real. Don&#8217;t use plagiarized content because readers hate that, use your own. Do more and more research and you will get the idea for fresh content.</p>\n<p>Keep in mind above SEO factors and build your own strategy to surpass your most crucial competitors.</p>\n<p><strong>It&#8217;s your turn now.</strong><br />\nIs it something you will try? Something you have tried? Do leave a comment.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/10-seo-ranking-factors-boost-google-rankings-2017/\">10 SEO Ranking Factors To Boost Google Rankings in 2017</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:95:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/10-seo-ranking-factors-boost-google-rankings-2017/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.