.solwininfotech.com/?p=22289\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:639:\"<p>With the holiday season around the corner, we wish you and your family a Merry Christmas and a great New Year ahead! We hope this year had a great time and we wish the same for upcoming year. Let us inform you about an amazing offer before you wrap for Christmas celebrations. As we all [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/news/christmas-special-offer-unbelievable-discounts-wordpress-magento-products/\">New Year Offer 2017 – 35% To 50% OFF On All WordPress &amp; Magento Products</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Sanjay Dabhoya\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3729:\"<p>With the holiday season around the corner, we wish you and your family a <strong>Merry Christmas</strong> and a great <strong>New Year</strong> ahead!</p>\n<p>We hope this year had a great time and we wish the same for upcoming year. Let us inform you about an amazing offer before you wrap for Christmas celebrations. </p>\n<p>As we all know that Christmas brings lots of happiness and joy to us, we thought why not add some more fun. At <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/about-solwin/\" target=\"_blank\">Solwin Infotech</a>, we are glad to announce a special offer on this auspicious occasion. Yes, We are offering <strong>flat 50% OFF</strong> on all our <strong>Magento</strong> and <strong>WordPress</strong> products.</p>\n<p>Work out on your blogs and websites that affected your business performance last year. As, we have already updated all our products to latest versions, Make a fresh start with our updated versions of <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/products/magento-2-extensions/\" target=\"_blank\">Magento 2 extensions</a> and <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/products/wordpress-themes/\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress themes</a>.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_22296\" style=\"width: 830px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/christmas-gift-box.jpg\" alt=\"Christmas Gift Box\" width=\"820\" height=\"340\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22296\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/christmas-gift-box.jpg 820w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/christmas-gift-box-300x124.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/christmas-gift-box-768x318.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/christmas-gift-box-500x207.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/christmas-gift-box-624x259.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/christmas-gift-box-350x145.jpg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Christmas Gift Box</p></div>\n<p>If you missed to grab <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/news/thanksgiving-deals-black-friday-cyber-monday-sales-2016/\" target=\"_blank\">Black Friday sale offer</a>, make sure not to miss this one. Such deals and offers are very rare and special. This offer can save you a lot of money on WordPress themes, plugins. Not only on WordPress, we are also offering this offer on all Magento products too.</p>\n<p>Treat yourself for the winter holiday party by grabbing this special offer. We promise to give you best Christmas gift every year.</p>\n<p>Let us inform you all that this amazing deal <strong>starts on 27th December 2016</strong> and it will <strong>end on 5th January 2017</strong>. To avail Christmas offer, purchase an item and go on cart page. Discount coupon code will automatically apply.</p>\n<p>We are offering <strong>35% discount</strong> for newly registered customers. For our prevailing customers we are giving them <strong>50% discount</strong>.</p>\n<p>Please reach us at <a href=\"mailto:info@solwininfotech.com\" target=\"_blank\">info@solwininfotech.com</a> to know more.</p>\n<p>We hope you liked our Christmas gift. We will come with more such offers in new year later. For now, enjoy this deal and have a happy time with your friends-families with yummy foods.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/news/christmas-special-offer-unbelievable-discounts-wordpress-magento-products/\">New Year Offer 2017 – 35% To 50% OFF On All WordPress &amp; Magento Products</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:120:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/news/christmas-special-offer-unbelievable-discounts-wordpress-magento-products/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:96:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"x