v1.4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:7;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"Blog Designer PRO WordPress Plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:8;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"Blog Designer WordPress Plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:9;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"Date Range Post Selection\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:10;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"Latest Update Blog Designer\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:11;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"New Features Blog Designer PRO\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:12;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"New Social Share Icon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:13;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"New Update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:14;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"New Update Blog Designer PRO\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:15;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"Post Slider Layouts\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:16;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Post Views\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:17;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"Template Color Preset\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:18;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"WordPress Plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/?p=22240\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:612:\"<p>We are excited to bring you several months of hard work and determination. Blog Designer PRO 1.4 is live now with most required features to enjoy. Blog Designer PRO 1.4 with the new upgrade has been our most successful update in the last 3 months we’ve been creating them. It helps us for future updates [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/blog-designer-pro-v1-4-live-now-useful-features/\">Blog Designer PRO v1.4 is Live Now With New Features!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Alkesh Miyani\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11379:\"<p>We are excited to bring you several months of hard work and determination. Blog Designer PRO 1.4 is live now with most required features to enjoy.</p>\n<p>Blog Designer PRO 1.4 with the new upgrade has been our most successful update in the last 3 months we’ve been creating them. It helps us for future updates and goals that will continue and motivate our developers to implement new creative ideas with Blog Designer PRO plugin. We would also like to say many thanks to our 400+ customers who gave us ideas surrounding the plugin.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>3 Unique Post Slider Layouts</h2>\n<div id=\"attachment_22248\" style=\"width: 830px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-slider-layouts.png\" alt=\"Blog Designer PRO WordPress Plugin\" width=\"820\" height=\"350\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22248\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-slider-layouts.png 820w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-slider-layouts-300x128.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-slider-layouts-768x328.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-slider-layouts-500x213.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-slider-layouts-624x266.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-slider-layouts-350x149.png 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Blog Designer PRO v1.4 &#8211; Slider Layouts</p></div>\n<p>Sometimes, Post Slider is most needed requirements for blog website and that&#8217;s why we introduced 3 new Sunshiny, Crayon and Sallet slider layouts. Those all contains unique design and easy implementation with Blog Designer plugin.</p>\n<p>You have to do is setup one time slider settings and slider layouts works automatically!</p>\n<h4>Slide Layout Features</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Slider Columns &#8211; 1 Column, 2 Columns &amp; 3 Columns</li>\n<li>Slider Effect &#8211; Fade &amp; Slide</li>\n<li>Slider to scroll &#8211; 1 Post, 2 Posts &amp; 3 Posts</li>\n<li>Display Slider Navigation</li>\n<li>Select Slider Navigation</li>\n<li>Display Slider Controls</li>\n<li>Slider Autoplay</li>\n<li>Slider Autoplay Intervals</li>\n<li>Slider Speed</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Single Post Layout</h2>\n<div id=\"attachment_22243\" style=\"width: 830px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-Single-Post-Layouts.jpg\" alt=\"Blog Designer PRO WordPress Plugin\" width=\"820\" height=\"425\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22243\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-Single-Post-Layouts.jpg 820w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-Single-Post-Layouts-300x155.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-Single-Post-Layouts-768x398.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-Single-Post-Layouts-500x259.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-Single-Post-Layouts-624x323.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-Single-Post-Layouts-350x181.jpg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Blog Designer PRO v1.4 &#8211; Single Post Layouts</p></div>\n<p>Blog Designer PRO 1.4 introduces a new upgrade layout system, giving you the ability to decorate single post pages. You can also design your single post pages based on category &amp; tags.</p>\n<h4>Why single post layouts required?</h4>\n<p>WordPress 4.7 announced a new feature as &#8220;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2016/11/03/post-type-templates-in-4-7/\" target=\"_blank\">Post Template</a>&#8221; and this new feature will give you capability to select different-different template for post single pages.</p>\n<p>This is really nice feature for WordPress users. But, every WordPress users are not developers. We think twice and update our single post layout structure for unlimited layouts. Now, there is no limit. You can create hundreds of or thousands of single post layout according to your requirements and then just select categories/tags for posts.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Template Color Preset</h2>\n<div id=\"attachment_22274\" style=\"width: 830px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-pro-color-preset.gif\" alt=\"Blog Designer PRO WordPress Plugin\" width=\"820\" height=\"350\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22274\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Blog Designer PRO &#8211; Color Preset</p></div>\n<p>Setting up colors is more difficult job for developers because they may not have an idea about color selection. They are finding appropriate or similar colors simultaneously for blog page. Why don&#8217;t we waste our timing to select colors?.. we understood your requirements and create color preset for all templates.</p>\n<p>Now, Blog Designer bundles with minimum 4 beautiful color presets for every blog templates. </p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>New social share icon style</h2>\n<div id=\"attachment_22279\" style=\"width: 830px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-Social-Share-Settings.jpg\" alt=\"Blog Designer PRO WordPress Plugin\" width=\"820\" height=\"495\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22279\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-Social-Share-Settings.jpg 820w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-Social-Share-Settings-300x181.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-Social-Share-Settings-768x464.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-Social-Share-Settings-500x302.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-Social-Share-Settings-624x377.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-Social-Share-Settings-331x200.jpg 331w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Blog Designer PRO v1.4 &#8211; Social Share Settings</p></div>\n<p>Blog Designer was provided only 1 social layout with default selection. Now, you may love so much to Blog Designer plugin because that default set increased with value 10x. Yes, you listen correct!!! We have now 10 default and unique social icon collection to setup your blog page with any design.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>First Sidebar Widget &#8211; Recent Posts</h2>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_22277\" style=\"width: 299px\" class=\"wp-caption alignright\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/BDP-Recent-Posts-289x300.png\" alt=\"Blog Designer WordPress Plugin\" width=\"289\" height=\"300\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-22277\" style=\"margin-left: 10px\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/BDP-Recent-Posts-289x300.png 289w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/BDP-Recent-Posts-192x200.png 192w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/BDP-Recent-Posts.png 359w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 289px) 100vw, 289px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">BDP &#8211; Recent Posts</p></div>We just started to create sidebar widgets for blog lovers. There are lots of possibilities to create sidebar widgets with unique features but we started for &#8220;<strong>Recent Posts</strong>&#8221; widget to enhance default widget functionality with latest trends.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nThere are several options to showcase your posts in sidebar based on most recent posts, most liked posts or most commented posts.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Post Views</h2>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_22278\" style=\"width: 328px\" class=\"wp-caption alignright\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/BDP-Post-Views.png\" alt=\"Blog Designer WordPress Plugin\" width=\"318\" height=\"58\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22278\" style=\"margin-left: 10px\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/BDP-Post-Views.png 318w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/BDP-Post-Views-300x55.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 318px) 100vw, 318px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">BDP &#8211; Post Views</p></div>Post Views allows you to display how many times a post had been viewed by the end user. There are 2 different parameters to show views.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Daily Views</li>\n<li>All Views</li>\n</ol>\n<p>The views are counted each time when user visit the single post link. Every unique visit increase counter by one.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Date Range Post Selection</h2>\n<div id=\"attachment_22282\" style=\"width: 830px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-blog-posts-within-time-period.jpg\" alt=\"Blog Designer PRO WordPress Plugin\" width=\"820\" height=\"312\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22282\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-blog-posts-within-time-period.jpg 820w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-blog-posts-within-time-period-300x114.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-blog-posts-within-time-period-768x292.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-blog-posts-within-time-period-500x190.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-blog-posts-within-time-period-624x237.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Blog-Designer-PRO-v1.4-blog-posts-within-time-period-350x133.jpg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Blog Designer PRO &#8211; Blog Posts within time period</p></div>\n<p>This plugin is developed to supercharge the value of all blog possibilities. Which type of blog posts series you want to display with the blog page or with any home page section. It will let you filter posts by a custom date range or by an already defined range.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Other useful features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Pocket &amp; Telegram Social share</li>\n<li>Media size selection option in Single Post Layout</li>\n<li>Import/export single layout</li>\n<li>Post order by &#8211; Author Name and Post Like in Blog and Archive Layout</li>\n<li>Author selection to get posts based on author in Blog Layout</li>\n<li>and Much more</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Upgrade your <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/wordpress-plugins/blog-designer-pro/\">Blog Designer PRO</a> plugin copy to version 1.4 and enjoy blogging with new features..!!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/blog-designer-pro-v1-4-live-now-useful-features/\">Blog Designer PRO v1.4 is Live Now With New Features!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:99:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/blog-designer-pro-v1-4-live-now-useful-features/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:36:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"